external_knowledge:
- "early months" refers to January and February;
- "last year" refers to the year 2022;
- "select salespeople" refers to those identified by specific IDs (1, 2, 3);
- "significant threshold" means an average revenue greater than $50,000.

sql:
SELECT SUM(total_revenue) AS overall_earnings
FROM sales_data
WHERE year_id = 2022;

SELECT SUM(total_sales) AS total_sales
FROM sales_data
WHERE year_id = 0;
